Tikar (nakwa Tikali, Tikar-East, Tikari, Tingkala) bụ Northern Bantoid, ọkara asụsụ Bantu na-asụ na Cameroon nke ndị Tikar na-asụ, yana ndị Pygmies Bedzan, bụ ndị na-asụ olumba nke asụsụ ahụ
Dị ka ọkà mmụta asụsụ na anthropologist Harry H
Johnston si kwuo, Semi-bantu na Bantu syntax na-atụ aro mmetụta sitere n'aka ndị Ijipt dynastic agwakọta na "asụsụ Negro na ọdịda anyanwụ na Central Sudan."
Obere ihe akaebe dịnụ na-egosi na ọ nwere njikọ chiri anya na asụsụ Mambiloid na Dakoid.
Enwere ike kewaa Tikar n'ụdị atọ, nke bụ Tikari, Tige, na Tumu.
